---
name: Realtime / streaming
category: Data
tags: [realtime, websocket, mqtt, stream]
description: Use the realtime edge kind for live data flows (WebSocket, SSE, MQTT). Animated dashes show movement.
---
# Realtime streaming pipeline

nodes:
  - id: sensor, kind: mobile,   label: Mobile
  - id: edge,   kind: firewall, label: Edge
  - id: bus,    kind: bus,      label: "Event Bus"
  - id: live,   kind: stream,   label: "Live View"

edges:
  - sensor -> edge, kind: realtime
  - edge   -> bus,  kind: realtime, label: "mqtt"
  - bus    -> live, kind: realtime, label: "ws"
